name: #TeamSeas Cleanup Game Simple
description:
This is a game to contribute the project of Mr Beast called Team Seas. Sorry for the early release date cause basically, my game is done. I really want to release this to Google Play but I don't have enough money, So here I have a GoGetFundMe Page to fund 25$ for the Google Play Store Publishing or you could just donate here if you like. You might be asking how this can contribute to the #TeamSeas Project? well, half of this game's revenue will be donated to the #TeamSeas Project.  Before I end this page, I know you, I mean why isn't there downloads in the game, I think you are just ignoring the page. Please, download now to support me, it would be the greatest pleasure I'll get. Thanks.
